    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My son and I went to Oaxaca about 30 years ago, when he was 12 or so. We didn&#39;t go to the coast, but we hit many of the same places in Oaxaca city and Monte Alban as well. Yes, some of those restaurants were there then! I loved walking down the hill from our hotel to the zocalo every morning to get breakfast with cafe con leche and fresh fruit. Happy memories!</p>
    </div>

