      <p>Hi Molly. That&#8217;s our house, Casa Sol a Sol, that you stayed at in Estacahuite!</p>
<p>So glad you enjoyed your stay! </p>
<p>The people that are staying there now read about it on your blog&#8230;this is their second time there!</p>
<p>We&#8217;re not good about planning ahead, so I&#8217;m writing this while sitting on a different Oaxacan beach, where we came to stay while the house is occupied. Can&#8217;t wait to get back there!</p>
<p>Our lovely renters had us over for breakfast a couple of days ago. It&#8217;s so much fun to see what other people do there&#8230;a different experience for everyone!</p>
<p>Come on back any time!</p>
<p>Megan</p>
